data.description: Stunning 3 BD, 2.5 BA custom built 2-story home in De Luz sits atop 10.09 acres with panoramic mountain views!  This hilltop retreat is completely private and has so much to offer!  Gorgeous open concept living space on main level pours with natural light, where you will find the kitchen with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, two ovens, tons of cabinet space for storage, walk-in pantry, reverse osmosis water system, French doors leading to the rear patio, the primary ensuite with dual sink vanity & spacious walk-in closet, a secondary bedroom, full bathroom and laundry room.  Take the unique spiral staircase up to the upper level to find the third bedroom and half bath in the tower with a Romeo and Juliet balcony to take in more views!  The lengthy driveway and carport offer plenty of space for parking.  This property is zoned for horses and has much opportunity for growth.  Completely move-in ready!  Schedule a tour today!
